| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6973 — Recovery Inhibition (securotrop)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: cabc1c39-2aee-511b-b9d6-49079b92e9b9"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
